thread.title: Chris Angie
thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Chris Angie

author: Chris Angie
title: Chris Angie
text: Lucky tackle box has such amazing customer satisfaction I recommend it to anyone and everyone. I checked the tracking and Canada post said it was delivered however I never received it. It must have got stolen or something. I was really upset cause' I am so excited for it every month. So I emailed Lucky Tackle Box and Nichole sent me another set for January and it totally made my day. Thank you so much guys! Love the products! - Christian :D
